OL,3,CZutons former guitarist attacked in
OL,4,Calleged 'hate-related assault'
OL,6,FA founding member of The Zutons has
OL,7,Fbeen attacked in an alleged hate-
OL,8,Frelated assault.
OL,10,FBoyan Chowdhury, a former member of
OL,11,Fthe Liverpool indie rock band, posted
OL,12,Fon social media claiming to have been
OL,13,Fracially attacked by a group of men on
OL,14,F21 March.
OL,16,FHe alleged they used racial slurs
OL,17,Fagainst him before he was struck on
OL,18,Fthe head by a piece of wood while out
OL,19,Fin Wavertree, Liverpool.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
