CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774271469
OL,3,CZutons former guitarist attacked in
OL,4,Calleged 'hate-related assault'
OL,6,FMerseyside Police say he sustained a
OL,7,Fserious head injury and required
OL,8,Fhospital treatment, following the
OL,9,Faltercation near Fieldway at around
OL,10,F2.15pm.
OL,12,FThe guitarist wrote on Instagram: "If
OL,13,FI hadn't of turned around I believe I
OL,14,Fwould've been struck on the back of
OL,15,Fthe head and dead right now."
OL,17,FThe Zutons star, known for singles
OL,18,Flike 'Why Won't You Give Me Your
OL,19,FLove?', shared photos of his injuries
OL,20,Fon social media.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
