PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774271469
OL,3,CZutons former guitarist attacked in
OL,4,Calleged 'hate-related assault'
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Debra Morley said:
OL,7,F"This was a shocking assault that has
OL,8,Fabsolutely no place in our communities.
OL,10,F"To racially abuse someone and then
OL,11,Fattack him with a weapon is abhorrent
OL,12,Fand I'm sure the public in Merseyside
OL,13,Fwill be just as appalled as we are
OL,14,Fabout what happened.
OL,16,F"An investigation is ongoing into this
OL,17,Fincident and we are appealing for
OL,18,Fanyone with information to come
OL,19,Fforward. If you saw this group of
OL,20,Fmales near Fieldway or witnessed the
OL,21,Fincident, then please come forward.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
