OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774271469
OL,3,CZutons former guitarist attacked in
OL,4,Calleged 'hate-related assault'
OL,6,F"Violence and hate crime will simply
OL,7,Fnever be tolerated in our communities.
OL,8,FWe have specially trained officers who
OL,9,Frespond to reports of hate crime with
OL,10,Fcompassion and sensitivity, ensuring
OL,11,Fthat every piece of information is
OL,12,Facted upon to bring offenders to
OL,13,Fjustice."
OL,15,FAnybody with information can contact
OL,16,Fpolice on their social media desk, or
OL,17,Fcall 101 quoting reference 26000226633.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
